            <span class="highlight">banking</span>
            meets<br />
            <span class="highlight">technology</span>
        </h1>
        <h4>A simpler banking experience for a simpler life.</h4>
        <button class="btn-text btn--scroll-to">
            Learn more &DownArrow;
        </button>
        <img src="assets/bank-with-tech.png" class="header-img" alt="Minimalist bank items" />
    </div>
</header>

<section class="section" id="section--1">
    <div class="section-title">
        <h2 class="section-description">Features</h2>
        <h3 class="section-header">
            Everything you need in a modern bank and more.
        </h3>
    </div>

    <div class="features">
        <img src="/assets/deeper_ai-powered-assistant.png" data-src="assets/ai-powered-assistant.png" class="features-img" alt="Minimalist bank items" height = "300" width = "300" />
        
        <div class="features-feature">
            <div class="features-icon"></div>
            <h5 class="features-header">Powered by Gen AI</h5>
            <li>
                Advanced Search capabilities.
            </li>
            <li>
                Recommendations for mutual funds, credit cards, fixed deposits and more.
            </li>
            <li>
                Trend Analysis to improve account health and explain expense forecast
            </li>
        </div>

        <div class="features-feature">
            <div class="features-icon"></div>
            <h5 class="features-header">AI-Powered Financial Assistant</h5>
            <li>
                Always by your side, ready to answer questions and guide you 24/7.
            </li>
            <li>
                Find what you need quickly and discover hidden financial opportunities.
            </li>
            <li>
                Get tailored advice based on your unique financial profile.
            </li>

        </div>
        <img src="/assets/deeper_insight.png" data-src="/assets/deeper_insight.png" class="features-img" alt="Minimalist bank items" height = "300" width = "300"/>
        <img src="/assets/Aurora.png" data-src="/assets/Aurora.png" alt="Credit card" class="features-img" height="250"/>
        <div class="features-feature">
            <div class="features-icon"></div>
            <h5 class="features-header">Personalized Credit Card, Just for You</h5>
            <p>
                Get a credit card tailored to your unique ideas.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="section" id="section--2">
    <div class="section-title">
        <h2 class="section-description">Operations</h2>
        <h3 class="section-header">
            Everything as simple as possible, but no simpler.
        </h3>
    </div>

    <div class="operations">
        <div class="operations-tab-container">
            <button class="btn operations-tab operations-tab-1 operations-tab-active" data-tab="1">
                <span>01</span>Instant Transfers
            </button>
            <button class="btn operations-tab operations-tab--2" data-tab="2">
                <span>02</span>Instant Loans
            </button>
            <button class="btn operations-tab operations-tab-3" data-tab="3">
                <span>03</span>Instant Investment
            </button>
        </div>
        <div class="operations-content operations-content--1 operations-content-active">
            <div class="operations-icon operations-icon-1"></div>
            <h5 class="operations-header">
                Cymbal lets you experience the speed of life with instant transfers
            </h5>
            <p>
                Say goodbye to waiting days for your money to arrive, and embrace the convenience of sending and
                receiving funds anytime, anywhere. Whether you're paying friends, family, or businesses, splitting
                bills, or settling expenses, Cymbal ensures your money gets where it needs to be, instantly and
                securely.
                With transactions completed within seconds and bank-level encryption safeguarding your information,
                Cymbal removes the friction from financial interactions, leaving you free to focus on what matters
                most.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="operations-content operations-content--2">
            <div class="operations-icon operations-icon-2"></div>
            <h5 class="operations-header">
                Breathe Easy with Cymbal's Low-Interest Loans
            </h5>
            <p>
                Needing a financial boost shouldn't mean high-interest burdens. Cymbal offers competitive interest
                rates and flexible repayment options, making loans accessible and affordable. Whether you're
                tackling personal needs, home improvement projects, or business ventures, Cymbal simplifies the loan
                process with fast approvals and convenient mobile-app management.
                Enjoy transparent loan terms, no hidden fees or prepayment penalties, and the peace of mind knowing
                you're working with a trusted partner in achieving your financial goals.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="operations-content operations-content--3">
            <div class="operations-icon operations-icon-3"></div>
            <h5 class="operations-header">
                Invest like a pro with Cymbal's Instant Investments
            </h5>
            <p>
                Take control of your financial future with Cymbal's Instant Investments. Invest in a wide range of
                assets, from stocks and bonds to ETFs and mutual funds, all with just a few taps. Start small with
                fractional shares or build a diversified portfolio tailored to your risk tolerance and goals. Get
                real-time market updates, track your performance, and automate investments for effortless wealth
                building.
                With Cymbal, there's no minimum investment amount, making financial growth accessible to everyone.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="section" id="section--3">
    <div class="section-title section-title-testimonials">
        <h2 class="section-description">Not sure yet?</h2>
        <h3 class="section-header">
            Millions of people are already making their lifes simpler.
        </h3>
    </div>

    <div class="slider">
        <div class="slide slide--1">
            <div class="testimonial">
                <h5 class="testimonial-header">
