                    No more wasting time in line: I can manage my finances anytime, anywhere with their
                    user-friendly mobile app.
                    No more hidden fees: Their transparent pricing structure means I always know exactly what I'm
                    paying for.
                    Cymbal has truly revolutionized my banking experience. I'm finally free from the shackles of
                    old-school banks and can now focus on what really matters achieving my financial goals.
                </blockquote>
                <address class="testimonial-author">
                    <img src="" alt="" class="testimonial-photo" />
                    <h6 class="testimonial-name">Shreyash Gupta</h6>
                    <p class="testimonial-location">
                        Bengaluru, India
                    </p>
                </address>
            </div>
        </div>

        <button class="slider-btn slider-btn-left">&larr;</button>
        <button class="slider-btn slider-btn-right">&rarr;</button>
        <div class="dots"></div>
    </div>
</section>

